channel.title: [Project Insanity] Error when connecting client to server
channel.description: This is for [Project Insanity] I downloaded a good server and client but the client that came with it wasn't fullscreen. So I downloaded a fullscreen client but it will not connect to the server? Which exact files for the server and client do i need to change the "ip" in?

item.title: [Project Insanity] Error when connecting client to server
item.dc:creator: @DaMatt17 DaMatt17
item.description:
@DaMatt17 wrote:

In your client.java search for no-ip and change it to 0.0.0.0
